title: TNOD User & Password Finder 1.4.2 beta3 (32 & 64Bits)
description:
News in version 1.4.2 beta3:

* Fixed the installer that you entered incorrect data from the servers.





NOD User & Password Finder - a program that every startup or on demand, 
dives into the Internet and looking for keys for ESET NOD32 Smart Security 
and ESET NOD32 Antivirus for all versions 2.5.x, 2.7.x, 3.x, 4.0. x, 4.2.x, 5.0.x, 
and automatically inserts them. The program also has the option to save the keys found in the text. 
And many other useful features. 

The procedure for treatment: 
Disable self-defense, run TNod User & Password Finder and wait until the installation license.

WARNING:

* ESET can detect these utilities as a false virus.

Add into exclusions, the paths.
